                            <comment id="13691809" author="xieliang007" created="Mon, 24 Jun 2013 09:10:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached is a trivial fix.&lt;br/&gt;
rssStub could be null while we hit ServiceException in tryRegionServerReport, then get it from createRegionServerStatusStub(), per Javadoc :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;@return master + port, or null if server has been stopped&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;so we can ensure rssStub == null only happened while current server was stopped. and a simple fix should be just fine.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
